Acknowledgment:

Rustle's transcript assembly pipeline is inspired by and aims for algorithmic
parity with StringTie (https://github.com/gpertea/stringtie), developed by
Mihaela Pertea, Geo Pertea, and colleagues at Johns Hopkins University.
StringTie is distributed under the MIT License:

  Copyright (c) 2019 Mihaela Pertea, Geo Pertea

The variation graph (VG) mode for gene family assembly, multi-mapping
resolution (EM, MFLP, flow), SNP-based copy assignment, and novel copy
discovery are original contributions by the Rustle authors.
